lih.kg/2068154</a></span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"adfba2d5bb7bc954eaa3084918451396d4f4dea0","tid":2068264,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:14:35.000Z","msg":"我仲等緊連登唔知乜撚野既出黎護航<br />\n結果無<br />\n連BLOCKED USER都唔見有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4ad349e35bdb0212a6cfc0b2dbb746133f728b","tid":2068264,"uid":50811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9074142a09fbcb1f31413677c58a9a7b7cc0f82","tid":2068264,"uid":13176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:15:47.000Z","msg":"黑警拉人，紅官審案<br />\n成班一丘之貉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ab494dc96e593baced26c0d952cb7c407c6785","tid":2068264,"uid":360404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:16:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03ac5e18ddac503ae3109